    "demand side.",
    "Therefore, in future research, a more efficient one-step method needs to be designed to improve processing efficiency and real-time performance to better meet the needs of practical applications.",
    "With the rapid development of large language models, identifying and preventing the spread of deceptive information and accurately capturing consumer preferences is particularly important.",
    "In response to this challenge, we focused on two core tasks: AI-generated review detection and consumer preference analysis.",
    "Building on the pretrained language model, we have proven the effectiveness of treating AI-generated review detection tasks as text classification tasks."
